      <h1>⚔️ Arena Guide</h1>
      <p class="page-lede">
        Welcome to the whirlpool waters at the deepest reach of the archipelago. <strong>Arena is
        LevelUp Land's competitive division</strong>, made up of multiple game worlds, each with its own
        theme and rules. The first world now open is <strong>NU World</strong> — a proving ground running
        entirely on BNB Smart Chain: 100 warriors enter, the draw is randomized on-chain, the victors are
        crowned, and the fallen become Spirits — yet hold the vote that decides the fate of the Epoch.
        This guide uses NU World as its example; when new worlds open, their own rules pages will apply.
      </p>
    </header>

    <blockquote>
      <p>
        NU World runs multiple battlefields at different ticket prices in parallel: a light battlefield
        at 1 USDT, alongside high-stakes battlefields at larger amounts. Rules, odds, and distribution
        ratios are identical across all battlefields, with prizes scaling proportionally with the ticket price.
        <strong>All amounts on this page use the 1 USDT battlefield as the example.</strong>
      </p>
    </blockquote>

    <h2>Quick Start: Enter in Five Steps</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Link your wallet</strong> — bind your BSC wallet address in your profile, and make sure it holds enough USDT (plus a small amount of BNB for on-chain gas fees).</li>
      <li><strong>Pick a battlefield</strong> — go to <code>/arena</code> and choose a round that is "On Sale" (battlefields at different ticket prices run in parallel). Each card shows the ticket price, current progress (e.g. "87/100 entered"), and the round's position within the Epoch (e.g. "Battle 3 / 11").</li>
      <li><strong>Buy a Battle Soul</strong> — purchase this round's ticket at that battlefield's price. Each address may buy 1 per round. Once the purchase succeeds, you receive an on-chain NFT: your Battle Soul.</li>
      <li><strong>Wait for the draw</strong> — once all 100 tickets sell out, the system requests a random number from Chainlink VRF and completes the draw. You can check the status any time under "My Holdings".</li>
      <li><strong>Reveal your fate</strong> — after the draw, claim your Battle Soul's result: the NFT reveals your tier of fate and your Spirit's form, and any prize lands in your wallet instantly.</li>
    </ol>

